description:
&lt;p&gt;Newcastle Hospitals is a CQC endorsed outstanding organisation with a local, national and international reputation for excellence. We are looking to recruit experienced health care assistants to join our hospital Staff Bank. In return we can offer valuable work opportunities/experience, opportunity to apply for NHS substantive employment, comprehensive training, NHS Pension contributions and accrued holiday pay.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our bank service aims to supply appropriately skilled staff to cover temporary shortages across both acute and community settings especially during the COVID 19 pandemic. Joining the bank provides an excellent opportunity for those who wish to gain insight and experience into diverse areas and specialities while providing you with the flexibility to choose your own working hours – various hours available part time up to full time hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for dedicated individuals to become part of our team of valued bank staff where you will play a crucial role in our ongoing service delivery within our outstanding organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
